root: ^CAT: And now you have a shotgun. Where are you finding this stuff?
^GRIM: Eh, just on the ground somewhere. Someone must have dropped it.
^CAT: Basura de unos, tesoro de otros. Too bad for them.
^Ha! If you weren't wearing platform shoes, you'd almost look intimidating with all those firearms.

c-0: ^ GRIM: I'll show you how intimidating I can be when I break my foot off in-
^CAT: See you at the next checkpoint!
c-1: ^ GRIM: Between the two of us, I'm pretty sure I'm still the cute one.
